# Logs Directory

This directory contains all system logs.

## Log Files

- `ingestion.log` - Main pipeline execution log
- `normalization.log` - Schema normalization events
- `gpu_usage.log` - GPU quota tracking (CSV format: date,minutes)
- `similarity.log` - Query and match events
- `audit.log` - Clinical audit trail (JSONL format)

## Retention

Logs are retained indefinitely for audit purposes.
Rotate manually if size becomes an issue.

## Format

Most logs: Standard Python logging format
`audit.log`: JSON lines, one entry per line
`gpu_usage.log`: CSV format
